{"tid":842847,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"乃木坂46討論區#90: 永遠支持西野七瀨","createTime":"2018-09-30T15:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T16:05:51.000Z","uid":34304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2c5a2ce1bbf382e3939e8830388dc9b587bd9a15","tid":842847,"uid":34304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:54:02.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">LIHK乃PO呼籲:<br />\n「永遠支持西野七瀨」</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dX0wleA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdX0wleA.jpg&h=a7d798b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46(Nogizaka46)</span> 是一個日本大型女子偶像團體，為另一著名女子團體AKB48的「官方對手／正式對手」（公式ライバル），因此其行銷策略與AKB48的姐妹團體&mdash;&mdash;SKE48、NMB48、HKT48等不同，但總製作人同樣是秋元康，且與其他姊妹團體之間仍常有跨團體的合作或競賽企畫。團體名字中的「46」讀作「Forty-six／フォーティシックス」，而不是讀作「四十六／よんじゅうろく」。包含一期生、二期與三期生在內，團體目前共有40名成員，而隊長為櫻井玲香。<br />\n乃木坂46是作為AKB48的「官方對手」而成立的女子團體，因此跟AKB48的「姊妹團體」（如SKE48等）不同。例如團體不像AKB48及其姊妹團體般擁有AKB48劇場、NMB48劇場等專屬表演場地。團體名稱中的「乃木坂」是唱片公司日本索尼音樂（SME）總部大樓的所在地。<br />\n根據秋元康所說，<span style=\"color: red;\">「46」象徵：「就算人數比AKB48少，也具有不遜於AKB48的幹勁</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">成員名單:</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nogizaka46.com/member/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nogizaka46.com%2Fmember%2F&d=4ehNFi2R%2FwCFrCvLfGYmR%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=2d981282\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nogizaka46.com/member/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">-NEWS-</div><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<br />\n舞台「あさひなぐ」 Blu-ray &amp; DVD<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ml98QBh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMl98QBh.jpg&h=4698d0b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n乃木坂46 21stシングル「ジコチューで行こう！」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bddqv6B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fbddqv6B.jpg&h=e0c24797&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乃木坂46「真夏の全国ツアー2017 FINAL！IN TOKYO DOME」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SJEvV0X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FSJEvV0X.jpg&h=e41070bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46成員列表 21ST VER.(最新)</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gKzXfSw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgKzXfSw.jpg&h=14e02090&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎新人加入</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://nogizaka46-dc.com/sort/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnogizaka46-dc.com%2Fsort%2F&d=4ehNFi2R%2FwCFrCvLfGYmR%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=eb8f308e\" target=\"_blank\">http://nogizaka46-dc.com/sort/</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請新/舊手足定期體檢，以便加入DD黨</span></span></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Q&amp;A</div></span></span><br />\n1）那乃木坂乃何許人也？<br />\n簡單來說，乃木坂是來自日本的偶像組合，演戲唱歌跳舞等全部都會參與，是正統全能型偶像。<br />\n<br />\n2）那裡可以購買乃木坂既有關產品（生寫、CD、海報、寫真集、演唱會等）？<br />\n一般來說，信和地庫會有存貨，不過價錢就...另外有不少商品需於官方WEBSHOP購入，不過這裡有機會提供代購,，要看看手足們的心情。<br />\n<br />\n3）這裡可否討論其他非46的成員？<br />\n我們一般不會阻止，但請適量討論。皆因這裡主要討論46GRP,你也可作理性討論，攻擊、黑其他成員,但請先作好世界大戰的準備。<br />\n<br />\n4）那麼我要如何見到乃木坂成員？<br />\n直接飛去日本參加握手會、演唱會，但不要幻想他會再來港，因香港已經柒出國際。詳細辦法請向手足查詢。<br />\n<br />\n5）除了46GRP,有什麼值得推薦?<br />\nNONE<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">TEMPLATE:</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/17WaT3I7dwYQdmaT85JQnAJAzfBc9EXMXLKGLlpllO2E/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F17WaT3I7dwYQdmaT85JQnAJAzfBc9EXMXLKGLlpllO2E%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=4ehNFi2R%2FwCFrCvLfGYmR%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=4d7756f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/17WaT3I7dwYQdmaT85JQnAJAzfBc9EXMXLKGLlpllO2E/edit?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"17bd3363b43965fa6a6fd314f30ebfea569e8f8f","tid":842847,"uid":200983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:55:15.000Z","msg":"又#90<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88042299a95459eeff277f06182c6baec0045e33","tid":842847,"uid":169468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:55:24.000Z","msg":"應該係#91喎ching"},{"pid":"987f32ee0f74f7a4ced9d2f0f061c944dc66e18f","tid":842847,"uid":63295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:55:36.000Z","msg":"hea咗啲喎清<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c86cf41c7cfa8cd2964e8fb759b068e9206fdc8","tid":842847,"uid":34304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:56:14.000Z","msg":"見一路無人開<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79561ed619ebdca0cda777bb866c40beba75d18","tid":842847,"uid":169468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:56:16.000Z","msg":"開過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b71b2a94808ff1f43cd9b